    tags: [
      "React",
      "TypeScript",
      "Tanstack Query",
      "Playwright",
      "SCRUM",
      "JIRA",
    ],
  },
  {
    company: "BIXION",
    role: "Medior Frontend Developer",
    period: "Aug 2021 — Present",
    description:
      "Through connections from my time at Brno University of Technology, I joined BIXION — a Czech startup founded by two passionate engineers that delivers time-lapse solutions worldwide. I wrote both my bachelor's and master's theses here. For my bachelor's thesis I built a management interface for their time-lapse systems in React and JavaScript with Material UI. Over time, dissatisfaction with that codebase and growing requirements led me to rebuild the entire application from scratch — this time with TypeScript, shadcn/ui, and Tailwind. I'm much prouder of what it became. Working alongside one colleague, with full freedom over the tech stack, I've also had the chance to experiment with tools like Biome, Bun, and oxc.",
    tags: [
      "React",
      "TypeScript",
      "Websockets",
      "Material UI",
      "shadcn/ui",
      "Tailwind",
    ],
  },
  {
    company: "RACOM",
    role: "Junior Frontend Developer",
    period: "Aug 2022 — Jun 2024",
    description:
      "RACOM is a company from my hometown with global reach, specializing in wireless data transmission technology for critical infrastructure. I worked on the user interface for administering their devices — a project where I got my first hands-on experience with Playwright and a sophisticated design system built on the open-source react-ui library, to which I also contributed a few commits.",
    tags: ["React", "TypeScript", "Playwright"],
  },
  {
    company: "RehiveTech & Brno University of Technology",
    role: "Junior Frontend Developer",
    period: "Jul 2018 — Oct 2022",
    description:
      "Strong academic results in my first semester earned me the opportunity to work directly within the faculty at Brno University of Technology. I came in with a foundation in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript from high school, but this is where I first encountered React — and I've been working with it ever since. Class components, mercifully, are behind us.",
    tags: ["JavaScript", "React", "Material UI", "SCSS"],
